INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('22', '	It was a bright, co ', '4', '	It was a bright, cold day in April and the clocks were striking thirteen. Winston Smith hurried home to Victory Mansions with his head down to escape the terrible wind. A cloud of dust blew inside with him, and the hall smelled of dust and yesterday''s food. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''bright'':4 ''co'':5', '''april'':8 ''blew'':35 ''bright'':4 ''clock'':11 ''cloud'':32 ''cold'':5 ''day'':6 ''dust'':34,44 ''escap'':27 ''food'':48 ''hall'':41 ''head'':24 ''home'':18 ''hurri'':17 ''insid'':36 ''mansion'':21 ''smell'':42 ''smith'':16 ''strike'':13 ''terribl'':29 ''thirteen'':14 ''victori'':20 ''wind'':30 ''winston'':15 ''yesterday'':46');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('23', '	At the end of the h ', '3', '	At the end of the hall, a poster covered one wall. It showed an enormous face, more than a metre wide: the face of a handsome man of about forty-five, with a large, black moustache. The man''s eyes seemed to follow Winston as he moved. Below the face were the words BIG BROTHER IS WATCHING YOU. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''end'':3 ''h'':6', '''big'':55 ''black'':36 ''brother'':56 ''cover'':9 ''end'':3 ''enorm'':15 ''eye'':41 ''face'':16,23,51 ''five'':32 ''follow'':44 ''forti'':31 ''forty-f'':30 ''hall'':6 ''handsom'':26 ''larg'':35 ''man'':27,39 ''metr'':20 ''moustach'':37 ''move'':48 ''one'':10 ''poster'':8 ''seem'':42 ''show'':13 ''wall'':11 ''watch'':58 ''wide'':21 ''winston'':45 ''word'':54');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('24', '	Winston went up the ', '2', '	Winston went up the stairs. He did not even try the lift. It rarely worked and at the moment the electricity was switched off during the day to save money for Hate Week. The flat was on the seventh floor and Winston, who was thirty-nine and had a bad knee, went slowly, resting several times on the way. Winston was a small man and looked even smaller in the blue overalls of the Party. His hair was fair and the skin on his face, which used to be pink, was red and rough from cheap soap, old razor blades and the cold of the winter that had just ended. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''went'':2 ''winston'':1', '''bad'':51 ''blade'':101 ''blue'':72 ''cheap'':97 ''cold'':104 ''day'':27 ''electr'':21 ''end'':111 ''even'':9,68 ''face'':86 ''fair'':80 ''flat'':35 ''floor'':40 ''hair'':78 ''hate'':32 ''knee'':52 ''lift'':12 ''look'':67 ''man'':65 ''moment'':19 ''money'':30 ''nine'':47 ''old'':99 ''overal'':73 ''parti'':76 ''pink'':91 ''rare'':14 ''razor'':100 ''red'':93 ''rest'':55 ''rough'':95 ''save'':29 ''seventh'':39 ''sever'':56 ''skin'':83 ''slowli'':54 ''small'':64 ''smaller'':69 ''soap'':98 ''stair'':5 ''switch'':23 ''thirti'':46 ''thirty-nin'':45 ''time'':57 ''tri'':10 ''use'':88 ''way'':60 ''week'':33 ''went'':2,53 ''winston'':1,42,61 ''winter'':107 ''work'':15');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('25', '	Inside his flat, a  ', '4', '	Inside his flat, a voice was reading out a list of figures for last year''s production of iron. The voice came from a metal square, a telescreen, in the right-hand wall. Winston turned it down, but there was no way of turning it off completely. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''flat'':3 ''insid'':1', '''came'':22 ''complet'':48 ''figur'':12 ''flat'':3 ''hand'':33 ''insid'':1 ''iron'':19 ''last'':14 ''list'':10 ''metal'':25 ''product'':17 ''read'':7 ''right'':32 ''right-hand'':31 ''squar'':26 ''telescreen'':28 ''turn'':36,45 ''voic'':5,21 ''wall'':34 ''way'':43 ''winston'':35 ''year'':15');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('26', '	He moved to the win ', '2', '	He moved to the window. Outside, the world looked cold. The wind blew dust and bits of paper around in the street and there seemed to be no colour in anything, except in the posters that were everywhere. The face with the black moustache looked down from every corner. There was one on the house opposite. BIG BROTHER IS WATCHING YOU, it said, and the eyes looked into Winston''s. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''move'':2 ''win'':5', '''anyth'':31 ''around'':19 ''big'':57 ''bit'':16 ''black'':43 ''blew'':13 ''brother'':58 ''cold'':10 ''colour'':29 ''corner'':49 ''dust'':14 ''everi'':48 ''everywher'':38 ''except'':32 ''eye'':66 ''face'':40 ''hous'':55 ''look'':9,45,67 ''moustach'':44 ''move'':2 ''one'':52 ''opposit'':56 ''outsid'':6 ''paper'':18 ''poster'':35 ''said'':63 ''seem'':25 ''street'':22 ''watch'':60 ''wind'':12 ''window'':5 ''winston'':69 ''world'':8');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('27', '	Behind him the voic ', '6', '	Behind him the voice from the telescreen was still talking about iron. There was now even more iron in Oceania than the Ninth Three-Year Plan had demanded. The telescreen had a microphone, so the Thought Police could listen to Winston at any time of the day or night. They could also watch him through the telescreen. Nobody knew how often they actually did that but everybody behaved correctly all the time because the Thought Police might be watching and listening. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''behind'':1 ''voic'':4', '''actual'':64 ''also'':53 ''behav'':69 ''behind'':1 ''correct'':70 ''could'':39,52 ''day'':48 ''demand'':29 ''even'':16 ''everybodi'':68 ''iron'':12,18 ''knew'':60 ''listen'':40,82 ''microphon'':34 ''might'':78 ''night'':50 ''ninth'':23 ''nobodi'':59 ''oceania'':20 ''often'':62 ''plan'':27 ''polic'':38,77 ''still'':9 ''talk'':10 ''telescreen'':7,31,58 ''thought'':37,76 ''three'':25 ''three-year'':24 ''time'':45,73 ''voic'':4 ''watch'':54,80 ''winston'':42 ''year'':26');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('28', '	Winston kept his ba ', '4', '	Winston kept his back to the telescreen. It was safer that way - they couldn''t see your face. He looked out over London, the biggest city in this part of Oceania. The nineteenth-century houses were all falling down. There were holes in the streets where the bombs had fallen. Had it always been like this? He tried to think back to the time when he was a boy, but he could remember nothing. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''ba'':4 ''kept'':2 ''winston'':1', '''alway'':54 ''back'':4,62 ''biggest'':25 ''bomb'':49 ''boy'':70 ''centuri'':35 ''citi'':26 ''could'':73 ''couldn'':14 ''face'':18 ''fall'':39 ''fallen'':51 ''hole'':43 ''hous'':36 ''kept'':2 ''like'':56 ''london'':23 ''look'':20 ''nineteenth'':34 ''nineteenth-centuri'':33 ''noth'':75 ''oceania'':31 ''part'':29 ''rememb'':74 ''safer'':10 ''see'':16 ''street'':46 ''telescreen'':7 ''think'':61 ''time'':65 ''tri'':59 ''way'':12 ''winston'':1');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('29', '	He stared at the Mi ', '3', '	He stared at the Ministry of Truth, where he worked. It was an enormous white building, three hundred metres high. You could see the white roof, high above the houses, even a kilometre away. From Winston''s flat it was just possible to see the three slogans of the Party written in enormous letters on the side of the building: ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''mi'':5 ''stare'':2', '''away'':34 ''build'':16,60 ''could'':22 ''enorm'':14,53 ''even'':31 ''flat'':38 ''high'':20,27 ''hous'':30 ''hundr'':18 ''kilometr'':33 ''letter'':54 ''metr'':19 ''ministri'':5 ''parti'':50 ''possibl'':42 ''roof'':26 ''see'':23,44 ''side'':57 ''slogan'':47 ''stare'':2 ''three'':17,46 ''truth'':7 ''white'':15,25 ''winston'':36 ''work'':10 ''written'':51');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('30', '	IGNORANCE IS STRENG ', '6', '	IGNORANCE IS STRENGTH ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''ignor'':1 ''streng'':3', '''ignor'':1 ''strength'':3');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('31', '	The Ministry of Tru ', '2', '	The Ministry of Truth was called Minitrue in Newspeak, the new language of Oceania. Minitrue, it was said, had more than three thousand rooms above the ground and a similar number below. The people there worked mainly on news and entertainment. High above the surrounding buildings, Winston could also see the Ministry of Peace, where they worked on war. It was called Minipax in Newspeak. And the Ministry of Plenty - Miniplenty - which was responsible for the economy. And he could see the Ministry of Love - Miniluv - which was responsible for law and order. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''ministri'':2 ''tru'':4', '''also'':49 ''build'':46 ''call'':6,62 ''could'':48,80 ''economi'':77 ''entertain'':41 ''ground'':27 ''high'':42 ''languag'':12 ''law'':91 ''love'':85 ''main'':37 ''miniluv'':86 ''minipax'':63 ''miniplenti'':71 ''ministri'':2,52,68,83 ''minitru'':7,15 ''new'':11 ''news'':39 ''newspeak'':9,65 ''number'':31 ''oceania'':14 ''order'':93 ''peac'':54 ''peopl'':34 ''plenti'':70 ''respons'':74,89 ''room'':24 ''said'':18 ''see'':50,81 ''similar'':30 ''surround'':45 ''thousand'':23 ''three'':22 ''truth'':4 ''war'':59 ''winston'':47 ''work'':36,57');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('32', '	The Ministry of Lov ', '4', '	The Ministry of Love was the really frightening one. There were no windows in it. Nobody could get anywhere near it unless they had business there. There were guards with guns in black uniforms even in the streets half a kilometre away. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''lov'':4 ''ministri'':2', '''anywher'':19 ''away'':42 ''black'':33 ''busi'':25 ''could'':17 ''even'':35 ''frighten'':8 ''get'':18 ''guard'':29 ''gun'':31 ''half'':39 ''kilometr'':41 ''love'':4 ''ministri'':2 ''near'':20 ''nobodi'':16 ''one'':9 ''realli'':7 ''street'':38 ''uniform'':34 ''unless'':22 ''window'':13');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('33', '	Winston turned roun ', '1', '	Winston turned round quickly. He smiled. It was a good idea to look happy when you were facing the telescreen. He went to his small kitchen. He had not had lunch in the canteen before he left work, but there was no food there except a piece of dark, hard bread for tomorrow''s breakfast. He poured himself a cup of colourless, oily gin and drank it down like medicine. It burned him inside, but he felt more cheerful afterwards. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''roun'':3 ''turn'':2 ''winston'':1', '''afterward'':80 ''bread'':51 ''breakfast'':55 ''burn'':72 ''canteen'':34 ''cheer'':79 ''colourless'':62 ''cup'':60 ''dark'':49 ''drank'':66 ''except'':45 ''face'':18 ''felt'':77 ''food'':43 ''gin'':64 ''good'':10 ''happi'':14 ''hard'':50 ''idea'':11 ''insid'':74 ''kitchen'':26 ''left'':37 ''like'':69 ''look'':13 ''lunch'':31 ''medicin'':70 ''oili'':63 ''piec'':47 ''pour'':57 ''quick'':4 ''round'':3 ''small'':25 ''smile'':6 ''telescreen'':20 ''tomorrow'':53 ''turn'':2 ''went'':22 ''winston'':1 ''work'':38');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('34', '	He went back to the ', '6', '	He went back to the living room and sat down at a small table to the left of the telescreen. It was the only place in the room where the telescreen could not see him. From a drawer in the table he took out a pen and a big diary with beautiful cream paper, which he had bought in an old-fashioned shop in a poor part of the town. Party members like Winston were not allowed to go into ordinary shops, but many of them did. It was the only way to get things like razor blades. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''back'':3 ''went'':2', '''allow'':78 ''back'':3 ''beauti'':52 ''big'':49 ''blade'':99 ''bought'':58 ''could'':32 ''cream'':53 ''diari'':50 ''drawer'':38 ''fashion'':63 ''get'':95 ''go'':80 ''left'':17 ''like'':74,97 ''live'':6 ''mani'':85 ''member'':73 ''old'':62 ''old-fashion'':61 ''ordinari'':82 ''paper'':54 ''part'':68 ''parti'':72 ''pen'':46 ''place'':25 ''poor'':67 ''razor'':98 ''room'':7,28 ''sat'':9 ''see'':34 ''shop'':64,83 ''small'':13 ''tabl'':14,41 ''telescreen'':20,31 ''thing'':96 ''took'':43 ''town'':71 ''way'':93 ''went'':2 ''winston'':75');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('35', '	Winston opened the  ', '5', '	Winston opened the diary. This was not illegal. Nothing was illegal, as there were no laws now. But if the diary was found they would punish him with death or with twenty-five years in a prison camp. He took the pen in his hand, then stopped. He felt sick. It was a decisive act to start writing. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''open'':2 ''winston'':1', '''act'':56 ''camp'':39 ''death'':29 ''decis'':55 ''diari'':4,21 ''felt'':50 ''five'':34 ''found'':23 ''hand'':46 ''illeg'':8,11 ''law'':16 ''noth'':9 ''open'':2 ''pen'':43 ''prison'':38 ''punish'':26 ''sick'':51 ''start'':58 ''stop'':48 ''took'':41 ''twenti'':33 ''twenty-f'':32 ''winston'':1 ''would'':25 ''write'':59 ''year'':35');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('36', '	Earlier that mornin ', '1', '	Earlier that morning, a terrible noise from the big telescreen at the Ministry of Truth had called all the workers to the centre of the hall for the Two Minutes Hate. The face of Emmanuel Goldstein, Enemy of the People, filled the telescreen. It was a thin, clever face, with its white hair and small beard, but there was something unpleasant about it. Goldstein began to speak in his sheep-like voice: criticising the Party, making nasty attacks on Big Brother, demanding peace with Eurasia. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''earlier'':1 ''mornin'':3', '''attack'':79 ''beard'':56 ''began'':65 ''big'':9,81 ''brother'':82 ''call'':17 ''centr'':23 ''clever'':48 ''criticis'':74 ''demand'':83 ''earlier'':1 ''emmanuel'':35 ''enemi'':37 ''eurasia'':86 ''face'':33,49 ''fill'':41 ''goldstein'':36,64 ''hair'':53 ''hall'':26 ''hate'':31 ''like'':72 ''make'':77 ''ministri'':13 ''minut'':30 ''morn'':3 ''nasti'':78 ''nois'':6 ''parti'':76 ''peac'':84 ''peopl'':40 ''sheep'':71 ''sheep-lik'':70 ''small'':55 ''someth'':60 ''speak'':67 ''telescreen'':10,43 ''terribl'':5 ''thin'':47 ''truth'':15 ''two'':29 ''unpleas'':61 ''voic'':73 ''white'':52 ''worker'':20');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('37', '	In the past (nobody ', '2', '	In the past (nobody knew exactly when) Goldstein had been almost as important in the Party as Big Brother himself, but then he had worked against the Party. Before he could be punished with death, he had escaped - nobody knew how, exactly. Somewhere he was still alive, and all crimes against the Party came from his teaching. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''nobodi'':4 ''past'':3', '''aliv'':47 ''almost'':11 ''big'':18 ''brother'':19 ''came'':54 ''could'':31 ''crime'':50 ''death'':35 ''escap'':38 ''exact'':6,42 ''goldstein'':8 ''import'':13 ''knew'':5,40 ''nobodi'':4,39 ''parti'':16,28,53 ''past'':3 ''punish'':33 ''somewher'':43 ''still'':46 ''teach'':57 ''work'':25');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('38', '	Behind Goldstein''s  ', '2', '	Behind Goldstein''s face on the telescreen were thousands of Eurasian soldiers. Oceania was always at war with either Eurasia or Eastasia. That changed, but the hate for Goldstein never did. The Thought Police found his spies every day. They were called ''the Brotherhood'', people said, although Winston sometimes asked himself if the Brotherhood really existed. Goldstein had also written a book, a terrible book, a book against the Party. It had no title; it was just known as the book. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''behind'':1 ''goldstein'':2', '''also'':59 ''although'':47 ''alway'':15 ''ask'':50 ''behind'':1 ''book'':62,65,67,81 ''brotherhood'':44,54 ''call'':42 ''chang'':24 ''day'':39 ''eastasia'':22 ''either'':19 ''eurasia'':20 ''eurasian'':11 ''everi'':38 ''exist'':56 ''face'':4 ''found'':35 ''goldstein'':2,29,57 ''hate'':27 ''known'':78 ''never'':30 ''oceania'':13 ''parti'':70 ''peopl'':45 ''polic'':34 ''realli'':55 ''said'':46 ''soldier'':12 ''sometim'':49 ''spi'':37 ''telescreen'':7 ''terribl'':64 ''thought'':33 ''thousand'':9 ''titl'':74 ''war'':17 ''winston'':48 ''written'':60');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('39', '	As Goldstein''s face ', '5', '	As Goldstein''s face filled the telescreen and Eurasian soldiers marched behind him, the Hate grew. People jumped up and down, shouting and screaming so they could not hear Goldstein''s voice. Winston was shouting too; it was impossible not to. A girl behind him, with thick, dark hair was screaming ''Pig! Pig!'' at Goldstein, and suddenly she picked up a heavy Newspeak dictionary and threw it at the telescreen. It hit Goldstein on the nose and fell to the floor. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''face'':4 ''goldstein'':2', '''behind'':12,44 ''could'':27 ''dark'':48 ''dictionari'':64 ''eurasian'':9 ''face'':4 ''fell'':78 ''fill'':5 ''floor'':81 ''girl'':43 ''goldstein'':2,30,55,73 ''grew'':16 ''hair'':49 ''hate'':15 ''hear'':29 ''heavi'':62 ''hit'':72 ''imposs'':39 ''jump'':18 ''march'':11 ''newspeak'':63 ''nose'':76 ''peopl'':17 ''pick'':59 ''pig'':52,53 ''scream'':24,51 ''shout'':22,35 ''soldier'':10 ''sudden'':57 ''telescreen'':7,70 ''thick'':47 ''threw'':66 ''voic'':32 ''winston'':33');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('40', '	Winston had often s ', '5', '	Winston had often seen this girl at the Ministry but he had never spoken to her. He did not know her name, but he knew she worked in the Fiction Department. He had seen her with tools so he guessed she was a mechanic on the story-writing machines. She was a confident-looking girl of about twenty-seven, and she walked quickly. She wore the narrow red belt of the Young People''s League tied tightly round her overalls. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''often'':3 ''winston'':1', '''belt'':72 ''confid'':55 ''confident-look'':54 ''depart'':31 ''fiction'':30 ''girl'':6,57 ''guess'':40 ''knew'':25 ''know'':20 ''leagu'':78 ''look'':56 ''machin'':50 ''mechan'':44 ''ministri'':9 ''name'':22 ''narrow'':70 ''never'':13 ''often'':3 ''overal'':83 ''peopl'':76 ''quick'':66 ''red'':71 ''round'':81 ''seen'':4,34 ''seven'':62 ''spoken'':14 ''stori'':48 ''story-writ'':47 ''tie'':79 ''tight'':80 ''tool'':37 ''twenti'':61 ''twenty-seven'':60 ''walk'':65 ''winston'':1 ''wore'':68 ''work'':27 ''write'':49 ''young'':75');
