INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('82', '	Today four messages ', '1', '	Today four messages had come through the smallest hole, onto his desk. The messages were about changes to the Times newspaper. For example, in Big Brother''s speech in the Times of 17 March, he had said that South India was safe. The Eurasians would attack North Africa. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''four'':2 ''messag'':3 ''today'':1', '''17'':33 ''africa'':48 ''attack'':46 ''big'':25 ''brother'':26 ''chang'':17 ''come'':5 ''desk'':12 ''eurasian'':44 ''exampl'':23 ''four'':2 ''hole'':9 ''india'':40 ''march'':34 ''messag'':3,14 ''newspap'':21 ''north'':47 ''onto'':10 ''safe'':42 ''said'':37 ''smallest'':8 ''south'':39 ''speech'':28 ''time'':20,31 ''today'':1 ''would'':45');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('83', '	This had not happen ', '2', '	This had not happened. The Eurasians had attacked South India, not North Africa. Winston had to re-write part of Big Brother''s speech so you could read in the Times for 17 March that Big Brother had known about the attack before it happened. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''happen'':4', '''17'':34 ''africa'':13 ''attack'':8,43 ''big'':22,37 ''brother'':23,38 ''could'':28 ''eurasian'':6 ''happen'':4,46 ''india'':10 ''known'':40 ''march'':35 ''north'':12 ''part'':20 ''re'':18 ''re-writ'':17 ''read'':29 ''south'':9 ''speech'':25 ''time'':32 ''winston'':14 ''write'':19');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('84', '	When Winston had fi ', '3', '	When Winston had finished, his changes to the Times went with the newspaper down the middle hole. A new edition would soon appear, with his changes. Every copy of the old edition would disappear. Destroyed. The message to Winston with the changes would disappear down the memory hole, to be burned. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''fi'':4 ''winston'':2', '''appear'':23 ''burn'':51 ''chang'':6,26,42 ''copi'':28 ''destroy'':35 ''disappear'':34,44 ''edit'':20,32 ''everi'':27 ''finish'':4 ''hole'':17,48 ''memori'':47 ''messag'':37 ''middl'':16 ''new'':19 ''newspap'':13 ''old'':31 ''soon'':22 ''time'':9 ''went'':10 ''winston'':2,39 ''would'':21,33,43');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('85', '	Every day newspaper ', '6', '	Every day newspapers, magazines, photographs, films, posters and books were all changed. The past was changed. The Party was always right. The Party had always been right. The Records Department, where they destroyed all the old copies of everything, was the largest department in the Ministry of Truth, but there was no truth. The new copies were not true and the old copies had not been true either. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''day'':2 ''everi'':1 ''newspap'':3', '''alway'':20,25 ''book'':9 ''chang'':12,16 ''copi'':37,56,63 ''day'':2 ''depart'':30,43 ''destroy'':33 ''either'':68 ''everi'':1 ''everyth'':39 ''film'':6 ''largest'':42 ''magazin'':4 ''ministri'':46 ''new'':55 ''newspap'':3 ''old'':36,62 ''parti'':18,23 ''past'':14 ''photograph'':5 ''poster'':7 ''record'':29 ''right'':21,27 ''true'':59,67 ''truth'':48,53');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('86', '	For example, the Mi ', '4', '	For example, the Ministry of Plenty had said they would make 145 million pairs of boots last year. Sixty-two million pairs were made. Winston changed 145 million to 57 million. So the Party had made five million more boots last year than they expected to. But it was possible that no boots at all were made last year. And it was possible that nobody knew or cared how many boots were made. You could read in the newspapers that five million extra pairs of boots had been made and you could see that half the people in Oceania had no boots. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''exampl'':2 ''mi'':4', '''145'':12,28 ''57'':31 ''boot'':16,41,54,72,87,103 ''care'':69 ''chang'':27 ''could'':76,93 ''exampl'':2 ''expect'':46 ''extra'':84 ''five'':38,82 ''half'':96 ''knew'':67 ''last'':17,42,59 ''made'':25,37,58,74,90 ''make'':11 ''mani'':71 ''million'':13,22,29,32,39,83 ''ministri'':4 ''newspap'':80 ''nobodi'':66 ''oceania'':100 ''pair'':14,23,85 ''parti'':35 ''peopl'':98 ''plenti'':6 ''possibl'':51,64 ''read'':77 ''said'':8 ''see'':94 ''sixti'':20 ''sixty-two'':19 ''two'':21 ''winston'':26 ''would'':10 ''year'':18,43,60');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('87', '	Winston looked arou ', '1', '	Winston looked around the office. A woman with fair hair spent all day looking for the names of people who had been vaporized. Each of them was, in Newspeak, an unperson. She took their names out of every newspaper, book, letter... Her own husband had been vaporized last year. She took his name out too. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''arou'':3 ''look'':2 ''winston'':1', '''around'':3 ''book'':40 ''day'':13 ''everi'':38 ''fair'':9 ''hair'':10 ''husband'':44 ''last'':48 ''letter'':41 ''look'':2,14 ''name'':17,35,53 ''newspap'':39 ''newspeak'':29 ''offic'':5 ''peopl'':19 ''spent'':11 ''took'':33,51 ''unperson'':31 ''vapor'':23,47 ''winston'':1 ''woman'':7 ''year'':49');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('88', '	People disappeared  ', '3', '	People disappeared from the newspapers when they were vaporized and they could also appear in the newspapers when they did not exist. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''disappear'':2 ''peopl'':1', '''also'':13 ''appear'':14 ''could'':12 ''disappear'':2 ''exist'':22 ''newspap'':5,17 ''peopl'':1 ''vapor'':9');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('89', '	Winston remembered  ', '4', '	Winston remembered Mr Ogilvy. He had appeared in the newspapers because he had led the sort of life the Party wanted. Ogilvy had joined the Spies at the age of six. At eleven he told the Thought Police that his uncle was a criminal. At seventeen he had been an organizer in the Young People''s League. At nineteen he had invented a new bomb which had killed thirty-one Eurasians when it was first tried. At twenty-three, Ogilvy had died like a hero, fighting the Eurasians. There were photographs of Ogilvy, but there had been no Ogilvy. Not really. The photographs were made at the Ministry of Truth. Ogilvy was part of a past that never happened. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''rememb'':2 ''winston'':1', '''age'':29 ''appear'':7 ''bomb'':65 ''crimin'':44 ''die'':84 ''eleven'':33 ''eurasian'':72,90 ''fight'':88 ''first'':76 ''happen'':121 ''hero'':87 ''invent'':62 ''join'':24 ''kill'':68 ''leagu'':57 ''led'':14 ''life'':18 ''like'':85 ''made'':107 ''ministri'':110 ''mr'':3 ''never'':120 ''new'':64 ''newspap'':10 ''nineteen'':59 ''ogilvi'':4,22,82,95,101,113 ''one'':71 ''organ'':51 ''part'':115 ''parti'':20 ''past'':118 ''peopl'':55 ''photograph'':93,105 ''polic'':38 ''realli'':103 ''rememb'':2 ''seventeen'':46 ''six'':31 ''sort'':16 ''spi'':26 ''thirti'':70 ''thirty-on'':69 ''thought'':37 ''three'':81 ''told'':35 ''tri'':77 ''truth'':112 ''twenti'':80 ''twenty-thre'':79 ''uncl'':41 ''want'':21 ''winston'':1 ''young'':54');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('90', '	Anything could be c ', '6', '	Anything could be changed. A dreamy man with hairy ears called Ampleforth re-wrote old poems until they supported everything the Party believed in. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''anyth'':1 ''c'':4 ''could'':2', '''ampleforth'':12 ''anyth'':1 ''believ'':24 ''call'':11 ''chang'':4 ''could'':2 ''dreami'':6 ''ear'':10 ''everyth'':21 ''hairi'':9 ''man'':7 ''old'':16 ''parti'':23 ''poem'':17 ''re'':14 ''re-wrot'':13 ''support'':20 ''wrote'':15');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('91', '	But all this work,  ', '6', '	But all this work, all these changes, were not the main work of the Ministry of Truth. Most workers in the Ministry were busy writing everything that the people of Oceania read or saw: all the newspapers, films, plays, poems, school books, telescreen programmes and songs, the Newspeak dictionaries and children''s spelling books. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''work'':4', '''book'':42,54 ''busi'':24 ''chang'':7 ''children'':51 ''dictionari'':49 ''everyth'':26 ''film'':38 ''main'':11 ''ministri'':15,22 ''newspap'':37 ''newspeak'':48 ''oceania'':31 ''peopl'':29 ''play'':39 ''poem'':40 ''programm'':44 ''read'':32 ''saw'':34 ''school'':41 ''song'':46 ''spell'':53 ''telescreen'':43 ''truth'':17 ''work'':4,12 ''worker'':19 ''write'':25');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('92', '	After his morning''s ', '4', '	After his morning''s work, Winston went to the canteen. It was full, very noisy and smelled of cheap food and the gin that was sold from a hole in the wall. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''morn'':3', '''canteen'':10 ''cheap'':19 ''food'':20 ''full'':13 ''gin'':23 ''hole'':29 ''morn'':3 ''noisi'':15 ''smell'':17 ''sold'':26 ''wall'':32 ''went'':7 ''winston'':6 ''work'':5');
