INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('127', '	''They thought he wa ', '6', '	''They thought he was a Eurasian spy,'' said Parsons. ''They noticed his shoes were different,'' he added proudly. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''thought'':2 ''wa'':4', '''ad'':17 ''differ'':15 ''eurasian'':6 ''notic'':11 ''parson'':9 ''proud'':18 ''said'':8 ''shoe'':13 ''spi'':7 ''thought'':2');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('128', '	Winston looked at t ', '6', '	Winston looked at the dirty canteen, looked at all the ugly people in their ugly overalls, ate the terrible food and listened to the telescreen. A voice from the Ministry of Plenty was saying that they were all going to get more chocolate - twenty grammes a week. Was he the only one who remembered that last week they got thirty grammes? They were getting less chocolate, not more. But Parsons would not remember. And even a clever man like Syme found a way to believe it. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''look'':2 ''winston'':1', '''ate'':17 ''believ'':85 ''canteen'':6 ''chocol'':43,66 ''clever'':77 ''dirti'':5 ''even'':75 ''food'':20 ''found'':81 ''get'':41,64 ''go'':39 ''got'':59 ''gramm'':45,61 ''last'':56 ''less'':65 ''like'':79 ''listen'':22 ''look'':2,7 ''man'':78 ''ministri'':30 ''one'':52 ''overal'':16 ''parson'':70 ''peopl'':12 ''plenti'':32 ''rememb'':54,73 ''say'':34 ''syme'':80 ''telescreen'':25 ''terribl'':19 ''thirti'':60 ''twenti'':44 ''ugli'':11,15 ''voic'':27 ''way'':83 ''week'':47,57 ''winston'':1 ''would'':71');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('129', '	Winston came out of ', '5', '	Winston came out of his sad dream. The girl with dark hair, who he remembered from the Two Minutes Hate, was at the next table. She was looking at him, but when he looked back at her she looked away again. Winston was suddenly afraid. Why was she watching him? Was she following him? Perhaps she was not in the Thought Police, but Party members could be even more dangerous as spies. How had he looked when the telescreen voice told them about the chocolate? It was dangerous to look disbelieving. There was even a word for it in Newspeak: facecrime, it was called. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''came'':2 ''winston'':1', '''afraid'':45 ''away'':40 ''back'':35 ''call'':104 ''came'':2 ''chocol'':85 ''could'':66 ''danger'':70,88 ''dark'':11 ''disbeliev'':91 ''dream'':7 ''even'':68,94 ''facecrim'':101 ''follow'':53 ''girl'':9 ''hair'':12 ''hate'':20 ''look'':28,34,39,76,90 ''member'':65 ''minut'':19 ''newspeak'':100 ''next'':24 ''parti'':64 ''perhap'':55 ''polic'':62 ''rememb'':15 ''sad'':6 ''spi'':72 ''sudden'':44 ''tabl'':25 ''telescreen'':79 ''thought'':61 ''told'':81 ''two'':18 ''voic'':80 ''watch'':49 ''winston'':1,42 ''word'':96');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('130', '	The girl had turned ', '6', '	The girl had turned her back to him again. At that moment the telescreen told them all to return to work and the three men jumped to their feet. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''girl'':2 ''turn'':4', '''back'':6 ''feet'':29 ''girl'':2 ''jump'':26 ''men'':25 ''moment'':12 ''return'':19 ''telescreen'':14 ''three'':24 ''told'':15 ''turn'':4 ''work'':21');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('131', '	Winston sat at the  ', '1', '	Winston sat at the table and opened his diary. He thought of his parents. He was, he thought, about ten or eleven years old when his mother disappeared. She was a tall, silent woman with lovely fair hair. He could not remember his father so well. He was dark and thin and always wore dark clothes. They had both been vaporized in the 1950s. His thoughts moved to other women and he started writing in the diary: ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''sat'':2 ''winston'':1', '''1950s'':64 ''alway'':53 ''cloth'':56 ''could'':40 ''dark'':49,55 ''diari'':9,77 ''disappear'':28 ''eleven'':22 ''fair'':37 ''father'':44 ''hair'':38 ''love'':36 ''mother'':27 ''move'':67 ''old'':24 ''open'':7 ''parent'':14 ''rememb'':42 ''sat'':2 ''silent'':33 ''start'':73 ''tabl'':5 ''tall'':32 ''ten'':20 ''thin'':51 ''thought'':11,18,66 ''vapor'':61 ''well'':46 ''winston'':1 ''woman'':34 ''women'':70 ''wore'':54 ''write'':74 ''year'':23');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('132', '	It was three years  ', '4', '	It was three years ago. It was on a dark evening, in a narrow side-street near one of the big railway stations. She had a young face with thick make-up. I liked the make-up. The whiteness and the bright red lips. No woman in the Party wore make-up. There was nobody else in the street and no telescreens. She said two dollars. I... ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''three'':3 ''year'':4', '''ago'':5 ''big'':22 ''bright'':45 ''dark'':10 ''dollar'':70 ''els'':60 ''even'':11 ''face'':29 ''like'':36 ''lip'':47 ''make'':33,39,55 ''make-up'':32,38,54 ''narrow'':14 ''near'':18 ''nobodi'':59 ''one'':19 ''parti'':52 ''railway'':23 ''red'':46 ''said'':68 ''side'':16 ''side-street'':15 ''station'':24 ''street'':17,63 ''telescreen'':66 ''thick'':31 ''three'':3 ''two'':69 ''white'':42 ''woman'':49 ''wore'':53 ''year'':4 ''young'':28');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('133', '	It was too difficul ', '5', '	It was too difficult to continue. Winston wanted to hit his head against the wall, to kick the table over and throw the diary through the window – anything to stop the memory of that night. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''difficul'':4', '''anyth'':29 ''continu'':6 ''diari'':24 ''difficult'':4 ''head'':12 ''hit'':10 ''kick'':17 ''memori'':33 ''night'':36 ''stop'':31 ''tabl'':19 ''throw'':22 ''wall'':15 ''want'':8 ''window'':27 ''winston'':7 ''–'':28');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('134', '	It was, of course,  ', '2', '	It was, of course, illegal to pay a woman for sex. But the punishment was about five years in a work camp, not death. The Party knew it happened. Some prole women sold themselves for a bottle of gin and the Party didn''t worry much about that. The Party wanted to stop love and pleasure in sex, not sex itself. A request to marry would be refused if a man and a woman found each other attractive. Sex, to the Party, was only necessary to make children. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''cours'':4', '''attract'':78 ''bottl'':37 ''camp'':22 ''children'':88 ''cours'':4 ''death'':24 ''didn'':43 ''five'':17 ''found'':75 ''gin'':39 ''happen'':29 ''illeg'':5 ''knew'':27 ''love'':54 ''make'':87 ''man'':71 ''marri'':65 ''much'':46 ''necessari'':85 ''parti'':26,42,50,82 ''pay'':7 ''pleasur'':56 ''prole'':31 ''punish'':14 ''refus'':68 ''request'':63 ''sex'':11,58,60,79 ''sold'':33 ''stop'':53 ''want'':51 ''woman'':9,74 ''women'':32 ''work'':21 ''worri'':45 ''would'':66 ''year'':18');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('135', '	He thought of Kathe ', '3', '	He thought of Katherine, his wife. Winston had been married. He was probably still married; if his wife was dead, nobody had told him. They had lived together for about fifteen months, nine, ten, eleven years ago. Katherine was a tall, fair-haired girl who moved well. She had an interesting face, until you found out that there was almost nothing behind it. She believed everything the Party said. She had sex only because it was her duty to try and have children. When no children came, they agreed to separate. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''kath'':4 ''thought'':2', '''ago'':37 ''agre'':90 ''almost'':61 ''behind'':63 ''believ'':66 ''came'':88 ''children'':84,87 ''dead'':20 ''duti'':79 ''eleven'':35 ''everyth'':67 ''face'':53 ''fair'':43 ''fair-hair'':42 ''fifteen'':31 ''found'':56 ''girl'':45 ''hair'':44 ''interest'':52 ''katherin'':4,38 ''live'':27 ''marri'':10,15 ''month'':32 ''move'':47 ''nine'':33 ''nobodi'':21 ''noth'':62 ''parti'':69 ''probabl'':13 ''said'':70 ''separ'':92 ''sex'':73 ''still'':14 ''tall'':41 ''ten'':34 ''thought'':2 ''togeth'':28 ''told'':23 ''tri'':81 ''well'':48 ''wife'':6,18 ''winston'':7 ''year'':36');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('136', '	Every two or three  ', '1', '	Every two or three years since then, Winston had found a prole woman who had agreed to have sex for money. But he wanted his own woman. He finished the story in his diary: ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''everi'':1 ''three'':4 ''two'':2', '''agre'':16 ''diari'':34 ''everi'':1 ''finish'':29 ''found'':10 ''money'':21 ''prole'':12 ''sex'':19 ''sinc'':6 ''stori'':31 ''three'':4 ''two'':2 ''want'':24 ''winston'':8 ''woman'':13,27 ''year'':5');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('137', '	When I saw her in t ', '6', '	When I saw her in the light she was quite an old woman. She had no teeth at all. But I had sex with her. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''saw'':3', '''light'':7 ''old'':12 ''quit'':10 ''saw'':3 ''sex'':23 ''teeth'':17 ''woman'':13');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('138', '	He had written it d ', '2', '	He had written it down at last, but it did not help. He still wanted to shout and scream. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''d'':5 ''written'':3', '''help'':12 ''last'':7 ''scream'':19 ''shout'':17 ''still'':14 ''want'':15 ''written'':3');
