INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('323', '	Winston had worked  ', '4', '	Winston had worked more than ninety hours in the last five days of Hate Week. Now he had finished and he had nothing to do, no Party work until tomorrow morning. Slowly, in the afternoon sunshine, he walked up a narrow street to Mr Charrington''s shop, watching for the Thought Police, but sure - although he had no reason to be sure - that he was safe. In his case, heavy against his legs, he carried the book, Goldstein''s book. He had had it for six days but had not looked at it yet. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''winston'':1 ''work'':3', '''afternoon'':35 ''although'':55 ''book'':77,80 ''carri'':75 ''case'':69 ''charrington'':45 ''day'':12,87 ''finish'':19 ''five'':11 ''goldstein'':78 ''hate'':14 ''heavi'':70 ''hour'':7 ''last'':10 ''leg'':73 ''look'':91 ''morn'':31 ''mr'':44 ''narrow'':41 ''nineti'':6 ''noth'':23 ''parti'':27 ''polic'':52 ''reason'':59 ''safe'':66 ''shop'':47 ''six'':86 ''slowli'':32 ''street'':42 ''sunshin'':36 ''sure'':54,62 ''thought'':51 ''tomorrow'':30 ''walk'':38 ''watch'':48 ''week'':15 ''winston'':1 ''work'':3,28 ''yet'':94');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('324', '	Tired but not sleep ', '6', '	Tired but not sleepy, he climbed the stairs above Mr Charrington''s shop. He opened the window and put the water on for coffee. Julia would be here soon. He took Goldstein''s book out of his case and opened it. Then he heard Julia coming up the stairs and jumped out of his chair to meet her. She put her brown tool bag on the floor and threw herself into his arms. It was more than a week since they had seen each other. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''sleep'':4 ''tire'':1', '''arm'':73 ''bag'':64 ''book'':34 ''brown'':62 ''case'':38 ''chair'':55 ''charrington'':11 ''climb'':6 ''coffe'':24 ''come'':46 ''floor'':67 ''goldstein'':32 ''heard'':44 ''julia'':25,45 ''jump'':51 ''meet'':57 ''mr'':10 ''open'':15,40 ''put'':19,60 ''seen'':83 ''shop'':13 ''sinc'':80 ''sleepi'':4 ''soon'':29 ''stair'':8,49 ''threw'':69 ''tire'':1 ''took'':31 ''tool'':63 ''water'':21 ''week'':79 ''window'':17 ''would'':26');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('325', '	''I''ve got the book'' ', '5', '	''I''ve got the book'', he said. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''book'':5 ''got'':3 ''ve'':2', '''book'':5 ''got'':3 ''said'':7 ''ve'':2');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('326', '	''Oh, you''ve got it? ', '6', '	''Oh, you''ve got it? Good,'' she said without much interest, and almost immediately bent down to make the coffee. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''got'':4 ''oh'':1 ''ve'':3', '''almost'':13 ''bent'':15 ''coffe'':20 ''good'':6 ''got'':4 ''immedi'':14 ''interest'':11 ''make'':18 ''much'':10 ''oh'':1 ''said'':8 ''ve'':3 ''without'':9');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('327', '	They did not talk a ', '2', '	They did not talk about the book again until they had been in bed for half an hour. It was evening and just cool enough to have a blanket over them. Julia was falling asleep by his side. Winston picked the book up from the floor and sat up in bed. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''talk'':4', '''asleep'':35 ''bed'':14,51 ''blanket'':29 ''book'':7,42 ''cool'':24 ''enough'':25 ''even'':21 ''fall'':34 ''floor'':46 ''half'':16 ''hour'':18 ''julia'':32 ''pick'':40 ''sat'':48 ''side'':38 ''talk'':4 ''winston'':39');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('328', '	''We must read it,''  ', '3', '	''We must read it,'' he said. ''You too. All members of the Brotherhood have to read it.'' ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''must'':2 ''read'':3', '''brotherhood'':13 ''member'':10 ''must'':2 ''read'':3,16 ''said'':6');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('329', '	''You read it,'' she  ', '6', '	''You read it,'' she said with her eyes shut. ''Read it to me, that''s the best way. Then you can explain it to me.'' ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''read'':2', '''best'':17 ''explain'':22 ''eye'':8 ''read'':2,10 ''said'':5 ''shut'':9 ''way'':18');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('330', '	The clock''s hands s ', '1', '	The clock''s hands said six, meaning eighteen. They had three or four hours ahead of them. He put the book against his knee and began reading: ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''clock'':2 ''hand'':4', '''ahead'':15 ''began'':26 ''book'':21 ''clock'':2 ''eighteen'':8 ''four'':13 ''hand'':4 ''hour'':14 ''knee'':24 ''mean'':7 ''put'':19 ''read'':27 ''said'':5 ''six'':6 ''three'':11');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('331', '	There have always b ', '6', '	There have always been three kinds of people in the world, the High, the Middle and the Low. The world has changed but society always contains these three groups. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''alway'':3 ''b'':4', '''alway'':3,25 ''chang'':22 ''contain'':26 ''group'':29 ''high'':13 ''kind'':6 ''low'':18 ''middl'':15 ''peopl'':8 ''societi'':24 ''three'':5,28 ''world'':11,20');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('332', '	''Julia, are you awa ', '1', '	''Julia, are you awake?'' said Winston. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''awa'':4 ''julia'':1', '''awak'':4 ''julia'':1 ''said'':5 ''winston'':6');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('333', '	''Yes, my love, I''m  ', '4', '	''Yes, my love, I''m listening.'' ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''love'':3 ''m'':5 ''yes'':1', '''listen'':6 ''love'':3 ''m'':5 ''yes'':1');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('334', '	The aims of the thr ', '3', '	The aims of the three groups are completely different. The High want to stay where they are. The Middle want to change places with the High. Sometimes the Low have no aim at all, because they are too tired from endless boring work to have an aim. If they do have one, they want to live in a new world where all people are equal. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''aim'':2 ''thr'':5', '''aim'':2,32,47 ''bore'':42 ''chang'':22 ''complet'':8 ''differ'':9 ''endless'':41 ''equal'':65 ''group'':6 ''high'':11,26 ''live'':56 ''low'':29 ''middl'':19 ''new'':59 ''one'':52 ''peopl'':63 ''place'':23 ''sometim'':27 ''stay'':14 ''three'':5 ''tire'':39 ''want'':12,20,54 ''work'':43 ''world'':60');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('335', '	At the beginning of ', '4', '	At the beginning of the twentieth century this equality became possible for the first time because machines did so much of the work. A centuries-old dream seemed to becoming true. But in the early 1930s the High group saw the danger to them of equality for all and did everything possible to stop it. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''begin'':3', '''1930s'':37 ''becam'':10 ''becom'':31 ''begin'':3 ''centuri'':7,26 ''centuries-old'':25 ''danger'':43 ''dream'':28 ''earli'':36 ''equal'':9,47 ''everyth'':52 ''first'':14 ''group'':40 ''high'':39 ''machin'':17 ''much'':20 ''old'':27 ''possibl'':11,53 ''saw'':41 ''seem'':29 ''stop'':55 ''time'':15 ''true'':32 ''twentieth'':6 ''work'':23');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('336', '	The individual suff ', '1', '	The individual suffered in ways that he had not suffered for centuries. Prisoners of war were sent into slavery or hanged. Thousands were sent to prison although they had broken no law. The populations of whole countries were forced to leave their homes. And all this was defended and even supported by people who said they believed in progress. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''individu'':2 ''suff'':3', '''although'':27 ''believ'':57 ''broken'':30 ''centuri'':12 ''countri'':37 ''defend'':48 ''even'':50 ''forc'':39 ''hang'':21 ''home'':43 ''individu'':2 ''law'':32 ''leav'':41 ''peopl'':53 ''popul'':34 ''prison'':13,26 ''progress'':59 ''said'':55 ''sent'':17,24 ''slaveri'':19 ''suffer'':3,10 ''support'':51 ''thousand'':22 ''war'':15 ''way'':5 ''whole'':36');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('337', '	The people who ente ', '4', '	The people who entered the new High group were from the professions: scientists, teachers, journalists. They used newspapers, radio, film and television to control people''s thoughts. When a television that could both send and receive information was invented, private life came to an end. Every individual, or at least every important individual, could be watched twenty-four hours a day. For the first time it was possible to force people to obey the Party and to share the Party''s opinion on all subjects. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''ent'':4 ''peopl'':2', '''came'':42 ''control'':24 ''could'':32,54 ''day'':62 ''end'':45 ''enter'':4 ''everi'':46,51 ''film'':20 ''first'':65 ''forc'':71 ''four'':59 ''group'':8 ''high'':7 ''hour'':60 ''import'':52 ''individu'':47,53 ''inform'':37 ''invent'':39 ''journalist'':15 ''least'':50 ''life'':41 ''new'':6 ''newspap'':18 ''obey'':74 ''opinion'':83 ''parti'':76,81 ''peopl'':2,25,72 ''possibl'':69 ''privat'':40 ''profess'':12 ''radio'':19 ''receiv'':36 ''scientist'':13 ''send'':34 ''share'':79 ''subject'':86 ''teacher'':14 ''televis'':22,30 ''thought'':27 ''time'':66 ''twenti'':58 ''twenty-four'':57 ''use'':17 ''watch'':56');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('338', '	After the 1950s and ', '6', '	After the 1950s and 1960s the danger of equality had been ended and society had re-grouped itself, as always, into High, Middle and Low. But the new High group, for the first time, knew how to stay in that position for ever. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''1950s'':3', '''1950s'':3 ''1960s'':5 ''alway'':21 ''danger'':7 ''end'':12 ''equal'':9 ''ever'':44 ''first'':34 ''group'':18,31 ''high'':23,30 ''knew'':36 ''low'':26 ''middl'':24 ''new'':29 ''posit'':42 ''re'':17 ''re-group'':16 ''societi'':14 ''stay'':39 ''time'':35');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('339', '	First, in the middl ', '1', '	First, in the middle years of the twentieth century, the Party made sure that it owned all the property- all the factories, land, houses, everything except really small pieces of personal property. This meant that a few people (the Inner Party) owned almost everything and the Middle and Low groups owned nearly nothing. There was therefore no hope of moving up in society by becoming richer and owning more. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''first'':1 ''middl'':4', '''almost'':43 ''becom'':65 ''centuri'':9 ''everyth'':25,44 ''except'':26 ''factori'':22 ''first'':1 ''group'':50 ''hope'':58 ''hous'':24 ''inner'':40 ''land'':23 ''low'':49 ''made'':12 ''meant'':34 ''middl'':4,47 ''move'':60 ''near'':52 ''noth'':53 ''own'':16,42,51,68 ''parti'':11,41 ''peopl'':38 ''person'':31 ''piec'':29 ''properti'':19,32 ''realli'':27 ''richer'':66 ''small'':28 ''societi'':63 ''sure'':13 ''therefor'':56 ''twentieth'':8 ''year'':5');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('340', '	But the problem of  ', '5', '	But the problem of staying in power is more complicated than that. In the past, High groups have fallen from power either because they have lost control of the Middle or Low groups or because they have become too weak, or because they have been attacked and beaten by an army from outside. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''problem'':3', '''armi'':51 ''attack'':46 ''beaten'':48 ''becom'':38 ''complic'':10 ''control'':27 ''either'':22 ''fallen'':19 ''group'':17,33 ''high'':16 ''lost'':26 ''low'':32 ''middl'':30 ''outsid'':53 ''past'':15 ''power'':7,21 ''problem'':3 ''stay'':5 ''weak'':40');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('341', '	After the middle of ', '4', '	After the middle of the century there was really no more danger from the Middle or Low groups. The Party had made itself stronger by killing all of its first leaders (people like Jones, Aaronson and Rutherford). By 1970 Big Brother was the only leader and Emmanuel Goldstein was in hiding somewhere. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''middl'':3', '''1970'':39 ''aaronson'':35 ''big'':40 ''brother'':41 ''centuri'':6 ''danger'':12 ''emmanuel'':47 ''first'':30 ''goldstein'':48 ''group'':18 ''hide'':51 ''jone'':34 ''kill'':26 ''leader'':31,45 ''like'':33 ''low'':17 ''made'':22 ''middl'':3,15 ''parti'':20 ''peopl'':32 ''realli'':9 ''rutherford'':37 ''somewher'':52 ''stronger'':24');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('342', '	The Party then kept ', '2', '	The Party then kept itself strong. The child of Inner Party parents is not born into the Inner Party; there is an examination, taken at the age of sixteen. Weak Inner Party members are moved down and clever Outer Party members are allowed to move up. Although proles do not usually move up into the Party, the Party always stops itself from becoming stupid or weak. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''kept'':4 ''parti'':2', '''age'':27 ''allow'':43 ''although'':47 ''alway'':59 ''becom'':63 ''born'':15 ''child'':8 ''clever'':38 ''examin'':23 ''inner'':10,18,31 ''kept'':4 ''member'':33,41 ''move'':35,45,52 ''outer'':39 ''parent'':12 ''parti'':2,11,19,32,40,56,58 ''prole'':48 ''sixteen'':29 ''stop'':60 ''strong'':6 ''stupid'':64 ''taken'':24 ''usual'':51 ''weak'':30,66');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('343', '	The Party has also  ', '1', '	The Party has also made attack from the outside impossible. There are now only three great countries in the world. They are always at war but none of them can win or even wishes to win these wars. Following the idea of ''doublethink'' the mind of the Party, which controls us all, both knows and does not know the aim of these wars. The aim is to use everything that a country produces without making its people richer. If people became richer, there would be an end to the world of the High, the Middle and the Low. The Low and the Middle would not wish to stay in their places and would not need to. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''also'':4 ''parti'':2', '''aim'':60,65 ''also'':4 ''alway'':23 ''attack'':6 ''becam'':81 ''control'':50 ''countri'':17,72 ''doublethink'':43 ''end'':87 ''even'':33 ''everyth'':69 ''follow'':39 ''great'':16 ''high'':93 ''idea'':41 ''imposs'':10 ''know'':54,58 ''low'':98,100 ''made'':5 ''make'':75 ''middl'':95,103 ''mind'':45 ''need'':115 ''none'':27 ''outsid'':9 ''parti'':2,48 ''peopl'':77,80 ''place'':111 ''produc'':73 ''richer'':78,82 ''stay'':108 ''three'':15 ''us'':51 ''use'':68 ''war'':25,38,63 ''win'':31,36 ''wish'':34,106 ''without'':74 ''world'':20,90 ''would'':84,104,113');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('344', '	The Middle and Low  ', '6', '	The Middle and Low are kept in their places by their belief in the wars that none of the three countries can win. So the Party has to end independent thought and make people believe everything they are told. The Party must know what every person is thinking, so they never want to end the war. War continues, always and for ever. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''low'':4 ''middl'':2', '''alway'':59 ''belief'':12 ''believ'':35 ''continu'':58 ''countri'':21 ''end'':29,54 ''ever'':62 ''everi'':45 ''everyth'':36 ''independ'':30 ''kept'':6 ''know'':43 ''low'':4 ''make'':33 ''middl'':2 ''must'':42 ''never'':51 ''none'':17 ''parti'':26,41 ''peopl'':34 ''person'':46 ''place'':9 ''think'':48 ''thought'':31 ''three'':20 ''told'':39 ''want'':52 ''war'':15,56,57 ''win'':23');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('345', '	People are given so ', '2', '	People are given somewhere to live, something to wear and something to eat. That is all they need and they must never want more. They are given work, but only the Thought Police do their work really well. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''given'':3 ''peopl'':1', '''eat'':13 ''given'':3,27 ''live'':6 ''must'':21 ''need'':18 ''never'':22 ''peopl'':1 ''polic'':33 ''realli'':37 ''someth'':7,11 ''somewher'':4 ''thought'':32 ''want'':23 ''wear'':9 ''well'':38 ''work'':28,36');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('346', '	All good things in  ', '1', '	All good things in the world of Oceania today, all knowledge, all happiness, come from Big Brother. Nobody has ever seen Big Brother. He is a face on posters, a voice on the telescreen. We can be sure that he will never die. Big Brother is the way the Party shows itself to the people. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''good'':2 ''thing'':3', '''big'':16,22,44 ''brother'':17,23,45 ''come'':14 ''die'':43 ''ever'':20 ''face'':27 ''good'':2 ''happi'':13 ''knowledg'':11 ''never'':42 ''nobodi'':18 ''oceania'':8 ''parti'':50 ''peopl'':55 ''poster'':29 ''seen'':21 ''show'':51 ''sure'':38 ''telescreen'':34 ''thing'':3 ''today'':9 ''voic'':31 ''way'':48 ''world'':6');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('347', '	Below Big Brother c ', '5', '	Below Big Brother comes the Inner Party, which is now six million people, less than 2% of the population of Oceania. Below the Inner Party comes the Outer Party. The Inner Party is like the mind of the Party and the Outer Party is like its hands. Below that come the millions of people we call ''the proles'', about 85% of the population. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''big'':2 ''brother'':3 ''c'':4', '''2'':16 ''85'':60 ''big'':2 ''brother'':3 ''call'':56 ''come'':4,26,50 ''hand'':47 ''inner'':6,24,31 ''less'':14 ''like'':34,45 ''million'':12,52 ''mind'':36 ''oceania'':21 ''outer'':28,42 ''parti'':7,25,29,32,39,43 ''peopl'':13,54 ''popul'':19,63 ''prole'':58 ''six'':11');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('348', '	A Party member live ', '1', '	A Party member lives under the eye of the Thought Police from birth to death. Even when he is alone he can never be sure he is alone. He will never make a free choice in his life. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''live'':4 ''member'':3 ''parti'':2', '''alon'':20,28 ''birth'':13 ''choic'':35 ''death'':15 ''even'':16 ''eye'':7 ''free'':34 ''life'':38 ''live'':4 ''make'':32 ''member'':3 ''never'':23,31 ''parti'':2 ''polic'':11 ''sure'':25 ''thought'':10');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('349', '	But there is no law ', '4', '	But there is no law and there are no rules. They are not necessary. Most people know what they must do - in Newspeak they are ''goodthinkers''. And since Party members were children they have been trained in three more Newspeak words: ''crimestop'', ''blackwhite'' and ''doublethink''. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''law'':5', '''blackwhit'':43 ''children'':32 ''crimestop'':42 ''doublethink'':45 ''goodthink'':26 ''know'':17 ''law'':5 ''member'':30 ''must'':20 ''necessari'':14 ''newspeak'':23,40 ''parti'':29 ''peopl'':16 ''rule'':10 ''sinc'':28 ''three'':38 ''train'':36 ''word'':41');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('350', '	Even young children ', '4', '	Even young children are taught ''crimestop''. It means stopping before you think a wrong thought. When you are trained in ''crimestop'' you cannot think a thought against the Party. You think only what the Party wants you to think. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''children'':3 ''even'':1 ''young'':2', '''cannot'':23 ''children'':3 ''crimestop'':6,21 ''even'':1 ''mean'':8 ''parti'':29,35 ''stop'':9 ''taught'':5 ''think'':12,24,31,39 ''thought'':15,26 ''train'':19 ''want'':36 ''wrong'':14 ''young'':2');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('351', '	But the Party wants ', '2', '	But the Party wants people to think different thoughts all the time. The important word here is ''blackwhite.'' Like many Newspeak words, this has two meanings. Enemies say that black is white - they tell lies. But Party members say that black is white because the Party tells them to and because they believe it. They must forget that they ever had a different belief. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''parti'':3 ''want'':4', '''belief'':64 ''believ'':53 ''black'':30,41 ''blackwhit'':18 ''differ'':8,63 ''enemi'':27 ''ever'':60 ''forget'':57 ''import'':14 ''lie'':35 ''like'':19 ''mani'':20 ''mean'':26 ''member'':38 ''must'':56 ''newspeak'':21 ''parti'':3,37,46 ''peopl'':5 ''say'':28,39 ''tell'':34,47 ''think'':7 ''thought'':9 ''time'':12 ''two'':25 ''want'':4 ''white'':32,43 ''word'':15,22');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('352', '	''Blackwhite'' and ''c ', '6', '	''Blackwhite'' and ''crimestop'' are both part of ''doublethink''. ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''blackwhit'':1 ''c'':3', '''blackwhit'':1 ''crimestop'':3 ''doublethink'':8 ''part'':6');
INSERT INTO "tbarticle" VALUES ('353', '	''Doublethink'' allow ', '2', '	''Doublethink'' allows people to hold two different ideas in their minds at the same time - and to accept both of them. In this way they can live with a changing reality including a changing past. The past must be changed all the time because the Party can never make a mistake. That is the most important reason. It is also important that nobody can remember a time better than now and so become unhappy with the present. By using ''doublethink'' the Party has been able to stop history, keep power and... ', '2015-11-22 00:00:00', 't', 'some image', '''allow'':2 ''doublethink'':1', '''abl'':85 ''accept'':18 ''allow'':2 ''also'':60 ''becom'':73 ''better'':68 ''chang'':30,34,40 ''differ'':7 ''doublethink'':1,80 ''histori'':88 ''hold'':5 ''idea'':8 ''import'':56,61 ''includ'':32 ''keep'':89 ''live'':27 ''make'':49 ''mind'':11 ''mistak'':51 ''must'':38 ''never'':48 ''nobodi'':63 ''parti'':46,82 ''past'':35,37 ''peopl'':3 ''power'':90 ''present'':77 ''realiti'':31 ''reason'':57 ''rememb'':65 ''stop'':87 ''time'':15,43,67 ''two'':6 ''unhappi'':74 ''use'':79 ''way'':24');
